WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.500
The Manta Transit logo appears over a blue background with an animated bus route line.

00:00:02.500 --> 00:00:05.000
The platform name "Manta Transit" appears in large letters, centered on screen.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.500
The route search interface appears with the origin and destination fields highlighted.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:10.000
Icons of a bus, a map, and a person in a wheelchair are shown together, closing with the on-screen slogan.
